nodes.text: Star Wars A–Z is an appendix of Star Wars: The Official Starships & Vehicles Collection magazine, appearing on the final page of each issue. It is an ongoing glossary of characters, weapons, and more from the film saga, with only a few alphabetized entries per issue.
